## Scriptorium Editor

A desktop HTML editor for [Scriptorium](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.melihozsoy.biblicalnotes) note backups.

### Download
👉 [**Download scriptorium-editor.html**](https://github.com/melihozsoy82/scriptorium-editor/raw/main/scriptorium-editor.html)

### Live version
https://melihozsoy82.github.io/scriptorium-editor/scriptorium-editor.html

### Usage
1. Enable **Developer Mode** in Scriptorium Settings
2. Connect phone via USB
3. Run: `adb forward tcp:8765 tcp:8765`
4. Open the editor → click **🔌 Live** → Connect
